  "remarks": "JSC Design Office for Shipbuilding Vympel (JSC DO Vympel) is one of Russia’s industrial and defence complexes that builds a wide range of ships of various classes and purposes, including carriers, tankers and support vessels for the Russian Navy. JSC DO Vympel is part of the State-owned shipbuilding company JSC United Shipbuilding Corporation.",
